WEBVTT

00:08.186 --> 00:11.515
And blessed is the fruit
of your womb, Jesus.

00:11.605 --> 00:15.673
Holy Mary, mother of God,
pray for us sinners

00:15.859 --> 00:18.843
now and at
the hour of our death.

00:18.979 --> 00:20.913
Amen.

00:27.089 --> 00:29.189
Are you coming?

00:32.073 --> 00:35.159
- Cora?
- Come here, Cora.

00:36.132 --> 00:37.581
Cora?

00:39.000 --> 00:45.074
